bilingual.target: 他们的朋友可能会赞助他们。
我们的活动有一个主要的赞助商。

bilingual.source: She agreed to sponsor the new art exhibition.
bilingual.target: 她同意赞助新的艺术展览。

bilingual.source: They are looking for a reliable sponsor.
bilingual.target: 他们正在寻找一个可靠的赞助者。

bilingual.source: As a sponsor, he provided a lot of help.
bilingual.target: 作为赞助者，他提供了很多帮助。

bilingual.source: The radio show is looking for a new sponsor.
bilingual.target: 这个广播节目正在寻找新的赞助商。

bilingual.source: Our sponsor helped us achieve this dream.
bilingual.target: 我们的赞助商帮助我们实现了这个梦想。

bilingual.source: The company decided to sponsor the local soccer team.
bilingual.target: 公司决定赞助当地的足球队。

bilingual.source: The company decided to sponsor the local football team.
bilingual.target: 公司决定赞助当地的足球队。

bilingual.source: The company's sponsor provided all the prizes.
bilingual.target: 这家公司的赞助商提供了所有的奖品。

yingyinNormal.en: So when you say you want to sponsor an attraction, what do you have in mind?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以当你想吸引赞助商，你脑中想起的是什么？

yingyinNormal.en: And when I do, we're talking big new sponsor, with private helicopters.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当我赢了之后，我就会得到新的赞助商，还有私人直升机

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, he's just sad cause you left town and went to your big race to win the Piston Cup that you've always dreamed about your whole life and get that big ol' sponsor and that fancy helicopter you was talking about.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为你走了，他感到很难过你去参加你的比赛，去赢取你梦寐以求的活塞杯，得到有钱的赞助商的赞助还有直升机接送。

yingyinNormal.en: MU's Greek Council. We sponsor the annual Scare Games.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怪大学生会，我们主办年度惊吓杯。

yingyinNormal.en: What emergency happened at the L.A. Zoo? That's a penguin I sponsor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在洛城动物园发生了什么紧急事故？我认养了一只企鹅。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm wondering if you'd sponsor me for the new-members thing tonight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想知道你能否为我担保，让我参加今晚的新会员派对。

yingyinNormal.en: Look at that, she remembers me. Okay, Nana, how would you like to be the sponsor for a very prestigious prize?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你看，她还记得我呢？那么，奶奶，你是否愿意资助一项极具影响力的大奖赛呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. How's that work? You find a member to sponsor you, come have some drinks with the committee, and they vote a few people in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是怎么回事？你找个会员为你担保，过来跟委员会喝点酒，他们会投票选出一些新会员。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: provide funds for a project or activity or the person carrying it out

examination_example.sentence: Such policies are largely self-serving measures that make their <highlight>sponsors</highlight> feelgood but do little to help average women.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些政策很大程度上是自私自利的措施，让赞助者感觉良好，但对普通女性几乎没有帮助。

examination_example.sentence: In South Carolina, a state-<highlight>sponsored</highlight> antismoking program called Rage Against the Haze sets out to make cigarettes uncool.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在南卡罗来纳州，一个由州政府赞助的名为“愤怒对抗阴霾”的禁烟项目开始让香烟变得不酷。

examination_example.sentence: A pair of bills <highlight>sponsored</highlight> by Massachusetts state Senator Jason Lewis and House Speaker Pro Tempore Patricia Haddad, provide a case in point.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 马萨诸塞州参议员和众议院临时议长提出的两项法案就是一个很好的例子。
